    "label" : "VERSE 1",
    "lines" : [ {
      "text" : "Fear not, little flock, from the cross to the throne,",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 5
      } ]
    }, {
      "text" : "From death into life He went for His own;",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "G",
        "position" : 5
      }, {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 37
      } ]
    }, {
      "text" : "All power in earth, all power above,",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 4
      }, {
        "chord" : "A",
        "position" : 24
      } ]
    }, {
      "text" : "Is given to Him for the flock of His love.",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 3
      }, {
        "chord" : "G",
        "position" : 37
      } ]
    }, {
      "text" : ""
    }, {
      "text" : "Only believe, only believe,",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 0
      } ]
    }, {
      "text" : "All things are possible, only believe;",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "G",
        "position" : 0
      }, {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 32
      } ]
    }, {
      "text" : "Only believe, only believe,"
    }, {
      "text" : "All things are possible, only believe.",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "G",
        "position" : 0
      }, {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 32
      } ]
    }, {
      "text" : "(Lord, I believe.....)"
    }, {
      "text" : "(Lord, I receive.....)"
    }, {
      "text" : "(Jesus is here.......)"
    }, {
      "text" : ""
    }, {
      "text" : "Fear not, little flock, He goeth ahead,",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 5
      }, {
        "chord" : "A",
        "position" : 34
      } ]
    }, {
      "text" : "Your Shepherd selecteth the path you must tread;",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 28
      } ]
    }, {
      "text" : "The waters of Marah He'll sweeten for thee,",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 4
      }, {
        "chord" : "G",
        "position" : 26
      }, {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 38
      } ]
    }, {
      "text" : "He drank all the bitter in Gethsemane.",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 3
      }, {
        "chord" : "A",
        "position" : 27
      }, {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 31
      } ]
    }, {
      "text" : ""
    }, {
      "text" : "Fear not, little flock, whatever your lot,",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 5
      } ]
    }, {
      "text" : "He enters all rooms, \"the doors being shut;\"",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "G",
        "position" : 3
      }, {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 38
      } ]
    }, {
      "text" : "He never forsakes, He never is gone,",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 3
      }, {
        "chord" : "A",
        "position" : 22
      } ]
    }, {
      "text" : "So count on His presence in darkness and dawn.",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 3
      }, {
        "chord" : "A",
        "position" : 32
      }, {
        "chord" : "D",
